@startuml SD-01
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #888888
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #444444
skinparam sequenceParticipantFontSize 12
skinparam sequenceMessageFontSize 11

title SD-01: Pencarian Ruangan Langsung

actor "Pengunjung\n(Browser)" as User #4A90D9
participant "Laravel\n(ChatbotController)" as Laravel #2E8B57
participant "ChatbotService\n(Laravel)" as Service #50C878
participant "Flask\n(app.py)" as Flask #E67E22
participant "ChatbotEngine\n(engine.py)" as Engine #8E44AD
participant "Search\n(search.py)" as Search #C0392B

== 1. User Mengirim Pesan ==
User -> Laravel : POST /chat\n{message: "dimana poli umum?"}
activate Laravel
Laravel -> Service : predict("dimana poli umum?")
activate Service
Service -> Flask : POST /predict\n{message: "dimana poli umum?"}
activate Flask

== 2. Deteksi Intent ==
Flask -> Engine : process("dimana poli umum?")
activate Engine
note right of Engine
  Clean text → hapus tanda baca
  Prediksi intent → "cari_ruangan"
end note

== 3. Pencarian Ruangan (Hybrid Search) ==
Engine -> Search : collaborative_search("poli umum")
activate Search
note right of Search
  1. Hitung skor semantik (S-BERT)
  2. Hitung skor overlap keyword
  3. Bonus nama ruangan cocok
  4. Pilih skor tertinggi
end note
Search --> Engine : best_room_id=5, score=0.87
deactivate Search

Engine --> Flask : (room_id=5, score=0.87, is_option=false)
deactivate Engine

== 4. Ambil Data Ruangan ==
Flask --> Service : {best_room_id: 5, intent: "cari_ruangan",\nresponse: "Poli Umum terletak di Gedung A...", match_score: 0.87}
deactivate Flask

Service -> Laravel : DataRuangan::find(5) + foto
activate Laravel #LightGreen
note right of Laravel
  Ambil data ruangan dari DB
  Ambil foto ruangan terkait
end note
Laravel --> Service : ruangan + foto
deactivate Laravel

Service --> Laravel : {message, rooms: [{id:5, nama:"Poli Umum", ...}], intent}
deactivate Service

== 5. Tampilkan Hasil ==
Laravel --> User : JSON response\n{message, rooms, intent}
deactivate Laravel

note over User
  Browser menampilkan:
  "Card Informasi Poli Umum"
  + Foto ruangan
  + Navigasi/arah
end note

@enduml
